# Build artifacts from the various standalone projects under Scripts/
# and elsewhere (Casket, CRun, LTree, ...). The dotfiles-backup module's
# own exclusion list (Nixos/config/github/exclusions.nix) is what
# actually controls what reaches the published GitHub copy -- this file
# is for local git hygiene / editor tooling that reads .gitignore
# directly, and should stay in sync with that list.
**/target

**/__pycache__
*.pyc
*.pyo
.mypy_cache
.pytest_cache
.ruff_cache
.venv
venv
.direnv

.DS_Store
